er\"><div class=\"x-col e2322-e11 m1si-f m1si-h\"><div class=\"x-row e2322-e12 m1si-5 m1si-6 m1si-9 m1si-d\"><div class=\"x-row-inner\"><div class=\"x-col e2322-e13 m1si-f m1si-g\"><div class=\"x-text x-content e2322-e14 m1si-j\"><p>With 225 years of technical expertise, we&rsquo;re always up for a challenge at Ormiston Wire.<\/p>\n<p>But when artist&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/mobile.facebook.com\/beecreativeandbuzz\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Suzanne Lynas<\/a>&nbsp;&nbsp;sought our advice on the best components for hanging a Megalodon shark from the ceiling of the Essex Wildlife Trust&rsquo;s&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.essexwt.org.uk\/blog\/30-days-wild\/2017\/06\/30\/day-29-fossil-hunting-naze\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Naze Centre,<\/a>&nbsp;we thought she might have bitten off more than she could chew.<span id=\"more-522\"><\/span><\/p>\n<p>The 12 metre-long, 65 ton bulk of the largest predator in vertebrate history makes Jaws look like a minnow &mdash; and would test the mettle of our specialist&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.ormiston-wire.co.uk\/wire-applications\/suspension-wire\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">suspension wire.<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Suzanne soon explained that we were 2.6 million years too late to see a real Megalodon &mdash; but installing the realistic model she had created would still be challenging for her team.<\/p>\n<p><strong>The Challenge<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Four-metre long shark sculpture suspended from a Glulam beam.<\/li>\n<li>Wooden object with canvas skin weighing 75kg, hanging above a public area &mdash; safety was paramount in this project.<\/li>\n<li>Client requested discreet metal cables and fittings for a smooth visual effect.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Our solution for Suzanne<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sturdy 878-1005 top fixing to secure tough 702-1502 suspension wire to Glulam beam.<\/li>\n<li>Wire secured to inside of shark using innovative&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.ormiston-wire.co.uk\/wire-products\/superclamps\/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">superclamp system.<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Shark secured at several points for security and stability.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>The result<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Suzanne said the Essex Wildlife Trust are &lsquo;really pleased with the aesthetics of the slimline fittings&rsquo; and her installation team are &lsquo;impressed with how easy the superclamps and other components were to fit and use.&rsquo;<\/p>\n<p>This superb shark model helps visitors dive into the murky but magnificent waters of prehistory &mdash; we&rsquo;re tempted to head down to The Naze Centre ourselves to see if we can be next to find a fossilised Megalodon tooth.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>If you want to chew over a tricky architectural or artistic installation with us, call 020 8569 7287 for a chat &mdash; we&rsquo;ll help your team turn your vision into reality.<\/strong><\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"x-col e2322-e15 m1si-f m1si-i\"><span class=\"x-image e2322-e16 m1si-k\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ormiston-wire.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Ormiston-Wire-Art-Installation-1-768x454-1.jpeg\" width=\"768\" height=\"454\" alt=\"Sample image\"><\/span><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"x-section e2322-e17 m1si-0 m1si-4 productDownloads\"><div class=\"x-row x-container max width e2322-e18 m1si-5 m1si-6 m1si-9 m1si-e\"><div class=\"x-row-inner\"><div class=\"x-col e2322-e19 m1si-f m1si-g\"><h2  class=\"h-custom-headline noTopMargin h2\" style=\"color: #193774;\"><span>Do you have an unusual application or usage for wire products?<\/span><\/h2><\/div><div class=\"x-col e2322-e21 m1si-f m1si-g\"><a class=\"x-anchor x-anchor-button has-graphic e2322-e22 m1si-l\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"\/contact-us\/\"><div class=\"x-anchor-content\"><span class=\"x-graphic\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i class=\"x-icon x-graphic-child x-graphic-icon x-graphic-primary\" aria-hid